Selecting Models Based on the Lowest Forecast RMSE

1. Analyize Series’ First 80% Training Set

Employment Training Set doesn’t pass the ADF test or the Ljung-Box test up to 24 lags. The correlogram suggests an AR(1) effect.

Inflation Training Set doesn’t pass the ADF test or the Ljung-Box test up to 24 lags. The correlogram suggests an AR(1) effect.

IPI Training Set doesn’t pass the ADF test or the Ljung-Box test up to 24 lags. The correlogram suggests an AR(1) effect.

Treasury Rate Training Set doesn’t pass the ADF test or the Ljung-Box test up to 24 lags. The correlogram suggests an AR(2) or AR(3) effect.
